            "id": "4580384",
            "title": "Canada to launch its first sovereign wealth fund with initial C$25B funding",
            "description": "<html><body><p data-eci=\"true\">Canada will launch its first sovereign wealth fund, with an initial federal contribution of C$25B ($18.3B) over three years, Prime Minister Mark Carney announced as part of a broader effort to build a more resilient and independent economy.</p>\n<p>The Canada Strong Fund will invest, alongside the private sector, in Canadian projects and companies across sectors including clean energy, critical minerals, agriculture and infrastructure. The returns will be reinvested to grow the fund.</p>\n<p>\"Many countries that are blessed with natural resources like Norway have sovereign wealth funds,\" Carney said. \"Canada hasn't had one, until now.\"</p>\n<p>\"And if you have a bit of extra money, we'll make it easy for you to invest in the fund to help build Canada strong for all,\" he added.</p>\n<p>A retail investment product will be launched to provide Canadians the option to invest and share in the returns. The government will consult on the design of this new instrument over the coming months. </p>\n<p>The Canada Strong Fund will <a href=\"https://www.canada.ca/en/department-finance/news/2026/04/canada-strong-fund.html\" rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"operate\">operate</a> at arm's length from the government, with its work guided by a CEO and an independent board of directors. </p>\n<p>Opposition Leader Pierre Poilievre criticized the move, calling it a sovereign debt fund. \"Norway, Singapore and Saudi Arabia run big budget surpluses, which they accumulate and put into their sovereign wealth funds,\" he said. \"Carney has no surplus and therefore no wealth to put in such a fund.\"</p>\n<div class=\"signup_widget_placeholder\"></div>\n</body></html>",
            "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/assets/og_image_1200-29b2bfe1a595477db6826bd2126c63ac2091efb7ec76347a8e7f81ba17e3de6c.png",
            "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/news/4580384-canada-first-sovereign-wealth-fund",
            "pub_date": "2026-04-28 18:17:15",
            "source": "seekalpha",
            "kind": 1,
            "language": "en"
        },
