            "title": "Spotify GAAP EPS of $3.45 beats by $0.51, revenue of $4.53B beats by $10M",
            "description": "<html><body><ul>\n<li>Spotify <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/pr/20489619-spotify-technology-s-a-releases-results-for-first-quarter-2026\">press release</a> (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\"><a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/SPOT\" title=\"Spotify Technology S.A.\">SPOT</a></span>): Q1 GAAP EPS of $3.45 <span> beats by $0.51</span>.</li>\n<li>Revenue of $4.53B (+7.9% Y/Y) <span> beats by $10M</span>.</li>\n<li>Premium Revenue growth of 10% Y/Y (or 15% Y/Y constant currency*), driven by subscriber gains; and</li>\n<li> Ad-Supported Revenue decline of 5% Y/Y (or increase of 3% Y/Y constant currency*)</li>\n<li>Unfavorable currency movements slowed Total Revenue Y/Y growth by ~600 bps vs. the ~670 bpsincorporated into our guidance</li>\n<li>Q1 MAU net adds of 10 milliondrove total MAUs to 761 million,accelerating to 12% Y/Y growth</li>\n<li>Premium Subscribers grew 9% Y/Yto 293 million, reflecting 3 millionquarterly net adds.</li>\n<li><figure class=\"regular-img-figure\" contenteditable=\"false\"><span><img alt=\"Spotify\" data-caption=\"\" data-original-src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/attachment/image/fd71ba10844996ec400d97f5d9b0bcbf.png\" data-rel=\"lightbox\" data-source=\"Spotify\" fetchpriority=\"high\" height=\"457\" sizes=\"(max-width: 767px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1023px) calc(100vw - 180px), 552px\" src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/attachment/image/fd71ba10844996ec400d97f5d9b0bcbf.png?io=w640\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/attachment/image/fd71ba10844996ec400d97f5d9b0bcbf.png?io=w750 750w,https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/attachment/image/fd71ba10844996ec400d97f5d9b0bcbf.png?io=w640 640w,https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/attachment/image/fd71ba10844996ec400d97f5d9b0bcbf.png?io=w480 480w,https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/attachment/image/fd71ba10844996ec400d97f5d9b0bcbf.png?io=w320 320w,https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/attachment/image/fd71ba10844996ec400d97f5d9b0bcbf.png?io=w240 240w\" width=\"900\"/></span><figcaption class=\"overlay-title\"><p class=\"item-caption\"><span class=\"item-source\">Spotify</span></p></figcaption></figure></li>\n<li>Shares <span>-8%</span> PM.</li>\n</ul>\n<div class=\"signup_widget_placeholder\"></div>\n</body></html>",
